				<textElement textAlignment="Justified">
					<font size="8"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[     3. I CERTIFY on my official oath that I have this _________________ paid in cash to each man whose appears the above roll, the amount set opposite his name, he having presented himself, established his identity, &amp; affixed his signature or thumb mark on the space provided therefore unpaid services are indicated by red ink through the column "Amount Paid".]]></text>
